mt: USiminoff uthe ukumaketha kwandisiwe ngemuva kokubonakala kwakhe ngo-2013 esiqeshini seShark Tank lapho iphaneli yokubonisa yenqabile ukusekela ngemali ukuqala kwayo.
ref: USminoff uthe izintengo zanyuka ngemva kokuvela kwakhe embukwisweni we-Shark Tank ngo-2013 lapho iphaneli yohlelo yenqaba ukusekela ibhizinisi ngezimali.

src: Abasemagunyeni bathi, ugqirha obesebenza kwiChildren’s Hospital of Pittsburgh, ePennsylvania uza kutyholwa ngokubulala okumasikizi emva kokuba umama wakhe efunyenwe efile kwibhuti yemoto yakhe ngoLwesithathu.
mt: Iziphathimandla zathi, kwiChildren ' a doctor s Hospital of pittsburgh yomsebenzi, futhi abulale izinengiso epennsylvania kutyholwa wathola unina washona emva ngolwesithathu kwibhuti yemoto yakhe.
ref: Udokotela owayesebenza eSibhedlela seziNgane sasePittsburgh, ePennsylvania uzobekwa icala lokubulala okuyisihluku ngemva kokuba unina etholakale eshonile endaweni yokubeka izimpahla ngemuva kwemoto yakhe ngoLwesithathu, kusho iziphathimandla e-Ohio.

src: Wavelisa izitampu ezingaphezu kwe-1 000 eSweden nakwamanye amazwe angama-28.
mt: Yena izitampu okukhiqiza ezingaphezu kuka-1 000 sweden nakwamanye amazwe may 28.
ref: Wenzele iSweden izitembu ezingaphezu kuka-1,000 kanye nezingu-28 zamanye amazwe.

src: Iphiramidi enkulu yenzelwe ukuhlonipha uFaro Khufu, kwaye uninzi lweepiramidi ezincinci, amangcwaba kunye neetempile zakhiwa ukuhlonipha abafazi bakaKhufu kunye namalungu osapho.
mt: The mbhoshongo omkhulu kafaro Khufu senzelwe ukuhlonipha, futhi lweepiramidi eziningi ezincane, futhi wakha ethempelini amathuna bakaKhufu ukuhlonipha abesifazane kanye namalungu omndeni.
ref: Umbhoshongo omkhulu ongunxa-ntathu wakhelwe ukuhlonipha uFaro uKhufu, futhi neminye imibhoshongo engunxa-ntathu emincanyana, amathuna, kanye namathempeli akhelwe ukuhlonipha inkosikazi kaKhufu kanye namalungu omndeni.

src: malunga nasekupheleni kwelixa le Middle Age I western Europe yaqalisa ukuzenzela esayo isimbo.Olona phuhliso lukhulu yeloxesha ngenxa yecrusade abantu baqalisa ukusebenzisa amaqhosha ekuqhosheni impahla.
mt: mayelana nasekupheleni kwehora le Middle Age I western Europe yaqala ukuzenzela esabekayo isitayela.Lona intuthuko yesiteshi sesikhathi ngenxa ye-crusade abantu baqala ukusebenzisa izinkinobho ekuqhosheni impahla.
ref: Ngasekupheleni kweNkathi Ephakathi intshonalanga Yurophu yaqala ukuthuthukisa isitayela sayo. Enye yentuthuko enkulu kakhulu yaleso sikhathi ngenxa yabalweli benkolo abantu baqala ukusebenzisa izinkinobho ukubopha izimpahla zokugqoka.

src: Iwebhusayithi yesikhululo ichaza umboniso "njengethiyetha yesikolo esidala enojikelezo olutshatsha nenengcwangu!"
mt: Iwebhusayithi yesiteshi ichaza umbukiso "njengethiyetha yesikole esidala enojikelezo olusha nengcwangu!"
ref: Iwebhusayithi yesiteshi ichaza uhlelo "njengomdlalo womsakazo odla ngoludala onokwaziswa okusha kwezobuchwepheshe!"

src: Umdlalo wokugqibela kolu luhlu uzakubanjelwa e-Ellis Park eRhawutini kwiveki ezayo, xa iSpringboks sidlala ne-Australia.
mt: Umdlalo wokugcina walolu chungechunge uzoba se-Ellis Park eGoli ngesonto elizayo, lapho amaBhokobhoko ezodlala ne-Australia.
ref: Umdlalo wokugcina womqhudelwano uzokwenzeka e-Ellis Park eGoli ngeviki elizayo, lapho ama-Springbok edlala ne-Australia.

src: Esona Sakhiwo sePhiramidi sase-Giza siso sodwa esisamileyo kwizimanga ezisixhenxe.
mt: Lesi Sakhiwo mbhoshongo base - futhi single esisamileyo kwizimanga eziyisikhombisa ye.
ref: I-Great Pyramid yase-Giza iyokuphela kwizimangaliso eziyisikhombisa esamile nanamuhla.

src: Eyasebusika imidlalo idumile kwiinginqgi zaseMantla, nama-Taliyani ekukhuphiswano lemidlalo yeHlabathi nemidlalo yee-Olympics.
mt: Eyasebusika imidlalo idumile ngezinqgi zaseNyakatho, namaTaliyani ekuncintisaneni imidlalo yeZwe nemidlalo yama-Olympics.
ref: Imidlalo yasebusika ithandwa kakhulu ezindaweni eziseNyakatho, lapho amaNtaliyane encintisana khona emidlalweni yamazwe onke kanye nasemidlalweni yama-Olimpiki.

src: Ngokwamapolisa, umqhubi wesithuthi esibethe umfoti akafane ajongane nezityholo zolwaphulo-mthetho.
mt: Ngokusho kwamaphoyisa, umshayeli wemoto eshaye umthwebuli wezithombe akavamile ukubhekana namacala obugebengu.
ref: Ngokusho kwamaphoyisa, cishe akunakwenzeka ukuthi umshayeli wemoto eshayise umthathi wezithombe amangalelwe.

src: Abantu abangaphezu kwezigidi ezine baya eRoma ukuya emngcwabeni.
mt: Bangaphezu kwezigidi zalaba bantu ngeke emngcwabeni eroma.
ref: Abantu abangaphezu kwezigidi eziyishumi baye enkonzweni yomngcwabo eRoma.

src: Izityalo zikwazi ukwenza ukutya ngenxa yelanga zisebenzisa inkqubo eyi-photosynthesis. Zikwenza nomthunzi.
mt: Izitshalo zingenza ukudla ngelanga zisebenzisa i-photosynthesis. Zakha nomthunzi.
ref: Izitshalo zenza ukudla kwazo nge-photosynthesis. Zibuye zenze nomthunzi.

src: Emveni kokwehla kwesiganeko, u ibson wathunyelwa kwisibhedlela kodwa wasweleka ngokukhawuleza emva koko.
mt: Ngemva kokwehla kwesigameko, ubson wathunyelwa esibhedlela kodwa wasweleka ngokushesha ngemva kwalokho.
ref: Ngemva kokuba kwenzeke ingozi, uGibson wayiswa esibhedlela kodwa washona ngokushesha ngemva kwalokho.

src: Ngenxa yoko, abenzi bomdlalo batshaya intsangu kwiqonga, kwaye nethiyetha ngokwayo ikhuthaza abaphulaphuli ukuba bajoyine.
mt: Ngenxa yalokho, abakhiqizi bomdlalo batshaya insangu esiteji, kanti nethiyetha uqobo ikhuthaza izethameli ukuba zijoyine.
ref: Njengomphumela, abaculi babhema insangu ye-cannabis esiteji, futhi nethiyetha ngokwayo igqugquzela izilaleli ukuba zihlanganyele.

src: Wayalela amagosa ukuba aye kwimoto yakhe eyi-Oldsmobile Intrigue eyaykumgama weenyawo eziyi-500.
mt: Wayala izikhulu zakhe ukuba ziye emotweni elandelayo-Usongo oldsmobile weenyawo eyaykumgama ha-500.
ref: Uqondise izikhulu kuyi-Oldsmobile Intrigue yakhe eyayikude ngamafidi angu- 500.

src: Ulimo lokuphila lulula, oludla ngokusebenzisa izichumisi, nesystem ezigciniweyo zembewu efumaneka kummandla edityaniswa nokujikelezisa udidi lwesityalo okanye naluphi na uhlobo ulwandisa isivuno.
mt: Ukulima kokuphila kulula, imvamisa usebenzisa umanyolo, nezinhlelo zembewu ezigciniwe ezitholakala esifundeni kuhlanganiswa nokuzungeza isitshalo noma yiluphi uhlobo olwandisa isivuno.
ref: Ukulimela ukuziphilisa indlela elula, ngovamile okususelwe ezintweni eziphilayo, kusetshenziswa imbewu egciniwe yasendaweni enezici ezingokwemvelo kuhlanganiswe nokushintshashintsha izilimo noma ezinye izindlela ezilula zokwenza umkhiqizo ube mningi.

src: UMlawuli wezoTshutshiso loLuntu, u-Kier Starmer QC, wenze ingxelo ngale ntsasa evakalisa ukutshutshiswa kwabo bobabini uHuhne noPryce.
mt: UMqondisi Wezokushushiswa Komphakathi, uKier Starmer QC, wenze isitatimende namhlanje ekuseni ememezela ukushushiswa kwabo bobabili uHuhne noPryce.
ref: UMqondisi wezoKubekwa Kwamacala koMphakathi, uKier Starmer QC, unikeze isitatimende namuhla ekuseni ememezela ukubekwa kwecala kukaHuhne kanye noPryce bobabili.

src: Ukuphumla phezu kweentaba ezisemantla e Mecca,umqolomba ulikheswa kwihlabathi liphela.
mt: Ukuphumula ezintabeni ezisenyakatho yeMecca, lo mhume uhlukanisiwe nomhlaba wonke.
ref: Umhume ohlezi phezu kwenye yezintaba zasenyakatho yase-Mecca, ukude kakhulu nomhlaba wonke.

src: Izithethe ezincinci zidibanisa abantu abacinga ngokufanayo baziva bengahoywanga yimigangatho yoluntu kwaye bayabavumela ukuba bakhulise ukuqonda kwesazisi.
mt: Izithuthi ezincane zihlanganyela abantu abacabanga ngendlela efanayo abazizwa benganakwa yimikhuba yomphakathi futhi bayabavumela ukuba bakhulise ukuqonda ngobuyena.
ref: Amaqembu ahlukile ahlanganisa abantu abazizwa benganakiwe yizimiso zomphakathi futhi abavumela ukwakha umuzwa wobuntu babo.
